225
00:21:19,916 --> 00:21:20,958
( gasps )

226
00:21:24,875 --> 00:21:28,291
I MUSTN'T.  RIGHT NOW,
I MUST TAKE THE TROOPS

227
00:21:28,375 --> 00:21:31,916
MY LORD ENTRUSTED TO ME
AND VENTURE STRAIGHT TO SATSUMA

228
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:34,750
TO FOIL TOYOTOMI'S
SINISTER DESIGNS.

229
00:21:34,833 --> 00:21:38,708
IF I CONCERNED MYSELF WITH
EVERY PERSON I CAME ACROSS...

230
00:21:43,791 --> 00:21:48,125
