231
00:22:03,791 --> 00:22:05,833
- ( Ichi whimpering )

232
00:22:10,041 --> 00:22:14,291
I-- I AM SO SORRY.

233
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:20,833
- THAT VOICE.
