234
00:22:24,166 --> 00:22:25,375
- THIS--

235
00:22:25,458 --> 00:22:29,125
THIS IS ALL

236
00:22:29,208 --> 00:22:32,125
MY FAULT.

237
00:22:32,208 --> 00:22:35,041
- ( theme music playing )
- ( singing in Japanese )

238
00:24:01,791 --> 00:24:04,000
- Ichi: THIS CASTLE,

239
00:24:04,083 --> 00:24:07,458
IT IS MY BROTHER'S
GRAVE MARKER.

240
00:24:07,541 --> 00:24:12,125
I BEG OF YOU,
PLEASE LET HIM REST IN PEACE.

241
00:24:12,208 --> 00:24:14,708
WHEN WE RETURN,

242
00:24:14,791 --> 00:24:16,791
